---
title: Beef & Roasted Veggie Farfalle with Parmesan & Parsley
description: In this dish, we've teamed the traditional Italian tomato sauce with seasoned beef mince and roasted veggies for a meal that
looks every bit as good as it tastes. First dibs gets an extra sprinkling of Parmesan!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tuscan-pork-roasted-veggie-spaghetti-90abb03c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/beef-roasted-veggie-spaghetti-6115f1c3ae2a8d207205b5fd-516a2497.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/beef-and-roasted-veggie-farfalle-6115f1c3ae2a8d207205b5fd
servings: 2
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  fat: 34.1 g
